Steps to get liferay portal docker image:
1. Install liferay-portal-7.0-ga6 from internet.
2. Extract it and keep it in particular directory.
3. Create dockerfile (as mentioned above).
4. Open CMD and go to this particular directory location and write command "docker build -t liferayimage:latest ." , this will build your liferay docker image.
5. Now run the container from built image by writing this command in CMD "dokcer run -it -p 8080:8080 liferayimage:latest". This will take few time.
6. Now you can access it by writing "http://localhot:8080" in your browser
